data.description: Welcome to the epitome of spacious and luxurious living in this impressive 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence. The home has a new roof, new ac water heater and new floors throughout.  As you step through the elegant foyer entrance, you are immediately captivated by the grandeur and sophistication that defines this home. The heart of this dwelling is undoubtedly the kitchen, a culinary haven that features a central island. This well-appointed space is not only a chef's dream but also a gathering place for family and friends. The open concept design seamlessly connects the kitchen to both the separate living and dining rooms, creating an ideal layout for entertaining and fostering a sense of togetherness. A dedicated family room enhances the comfort and functionality of the home, providing a cozy space for relaxation and shared moments. The convenience of a bedroom on the main level adds versatility, making it an ideal guest room, home office, or a private retreat for multi-generational living. Ascend to the upper level to discover the true sanctuary of the home—a large master suite that exudes luxury and tranquility. The master bathroom is a retreat within itself, boasting a double vanity, a separate tub for indulgent soaking, and a shower for a spa-like experience. This master suite is designed to provide a private haven for rest and rejuvenation. Adding to the allure of this residence is an extra-large bonus room, offering endless possibilities for use. Whether it becomes a home theater, a playroom, a fitness area, or a versatile entertainment space, this room allows for creativity and personalization. With a total of five bedrooms and three bathrooms, this home provides ample space for family members, guests, and various lifestyle needs. The thoughtful design, high-end finishes, and attention to detail make this home an exquisite retreat for those seeking both elegance and functionality.
